        <p class="pcard-brand">Onnit</p>
        <h3 class="pcard-name">Alpha Brain Gummies</h3>
        <div class="pcard-stars">
          <span class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9734;</span>
          <span class="rating-val">4.3</span>
          <span class="review-ct">(6,800 reviews)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pcard-specs">
          <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Key Ingredients</strong><span>L-Theanine, Alpha-GPC, Bacopa, Phosphatidylserine</span></div>
          <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Approach</strong><span>Multi-pathway cognitive enhancement</span></div>
          <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Clinical</strong><span>Published RCT on Alpha Brain formula</span></div>
          <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Caffeine</strong><span>None — stimulant-free</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pcard-price">
          <span class="price">$34.95</span>
          <span class="per-serv">$1.17/day (30ct)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pcard-pros-cons">
          <div class="pcard-pros">
            <h4>Pros</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>The only nootropic formula with a published, peer-reviewed clinical trial</li>
              <li>Multi-pathway approach: acetylcholine + alpha waves + memory consolidation</li>
              <li>Caffeine-free — no jitters, no crash, no tolerance buildup</li>
              <li>Backed by the Onnit brand with decades of sports nutrition credibility</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-cons">
            <h4>Cons</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Proprietary blend obscures individual ingredient doses</li>
              <li>Premium pricing at $1.17/day for 30 servings</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pcard-ctas">
          <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Onnit+Alpha+Brain+Gummies&tag=gummyguide-20" class="btn-cta" target="_blank" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener">Check Price on Amazon</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>Alpha Brain is the most clinically tested nootropic formula on the market. A 2016 randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled trial published in the <em>Journal of the International Society of Sports Nutrition</em> found that the Alpha Brain formula significantly improved verbal memory and executive function compared to placebo over 6 weeks. The gummy format delivers the same multi-pathway formula in a portable, pleasant-tasting format.</p>

