        <span class="pcard-badge">Best for Long-Term</span>
        <span class="pcard-num">#2</span>
        <img src="/images/products/fungies-lions-mane.webp" alt="Fungies Lion's Mane Focus Gummies" width="260" height="260" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="pcard-body">
        <p class="pcard-brand">Fungies</p>
        <h3 class="pcard-name">Lion's Mane Mushroom Gummies</h3>
        <div class="pcard-stars">
