          <span class="price">$24.99</span>
          <span class="per-serv">$0.83/day</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pcard-ctas">
          <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Fungies+Lions+Mane+Gummies&tag=gummyguide-20" class="btn-cta" target="_blank" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener">Check Price on Amazon</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>For long-term cognitive enhancement through neuroplasticity, lion's mane is the standout ingredient. Fungies uses 100% fruiting body extract (not mycelium-on-grain) standardized to over 20% beta-glucans. A 2009 study found significant cognitive improvements in adults 50-80 after 16 weeks. Pair with L-theanine for both immediate and cumulative benefits. For the full lion's mane breakdown, see our <a href="/mushroom/lions-mane-gummies/">lion's mane gummies</a> guide.</p>

    <div class="pcard" id="olly">
      <div class="pcard-top">
